⍝ Magnitude.tc
⍝ ════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: B numeric; Z numeric real
      ⍝ inv: ∣B ←→ B⌈|B   (for real B: max(B,|B|) = |B|)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,5) (,0 0 1 0 0)
      (|B) ≡ B⌈|B
1
      ⍝ inv: ∣B ←→ (B×+B)*.5   (for all B: sqrt of B times conjugate)
      (|B) ≡ (B×+B)*.5
1
      ⍝ inv: ∣B ←→ ((RE*2)+IM*2)*.5  for complex B=RE+0J1×IM
      RE ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 0 1 0 0)
      IM ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 0 1 0 0)
      B ← RE+0J1×IM
      (|B) ≡ ((RE*2)+IM*2)*.5
1
